{"tid":1319441,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"恐怖！人踩人清場行動部署","createTime":"2019-07-15T07:10:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T15:39:26.000Z","uid":261166,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"96e4d0a760af4ecbeac522b8d08a8838ea217404","tid":1319441,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T07:10:09.000Z","msg":"繼上次中信有不反對通知書，<br />\n警察兩邊包圍放催淚彈，<br />\n引起騷動，險導致人踩人。<br />\n<br />\n噚晚，警察又係多方包圍驅逐，<br />\n再係大會堂有不反對通知書下圍人驅人，<br />\n引致未能離開的無辜街坊巿民恐慌，<br />\n差 d 又攪到人踩人。（睇片頭幾十秒就知：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XWtLmf50G6g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXWtLmf50G6g&d=Nl%2Bce6%2FxXxAB2W4e8qnvdodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=3fc65c54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XWtLmf50G6g</a> ）<br />\n<br />\n年長香港巿民不會忘記蘭桂坊人踩人慘劇，<br />\n全港管理人流經驗最豐富是警察！<br />\n最清楚疏散唔到的危險！<br />\n<br />\n有乜可能係上次受輿論責難後，<br />\n竟然短時間內一而再，再而三用類近手法清場，<br />\n有理由<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">懷疑警方克意制造混亂，<br />\n甚至不惜引發人踩人！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目的係於不開一槍下，引發人踩人，<br />\n後果係導致數以百計死傷！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n強烈要求警方，不要採用無差別血腥清場行動！<br />\n呼喻前線警員不要執行屠殺任務！"},{"pid":"0cce100d4a89f1ce3521a5b50c38e59ce1be435a","tid":1319441,"uid":261166,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T07:16:17.000Z","msg":"義仕為維持商場或示威地點安全及秩序使用武力，<br />\n<br />\n以阻止人踩人危險發生，實非不得已，不應受譴責！"},{"pid":"c0ec7afecbcb0a6f898510bf58588db0481c0944","tid":1319441,"uid":261166,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:36:38.000Z","msg":"昨日新聞所見，商場原本平靜和諧！<br />\n保安及安全都無問題，秩序良好！<br />\n<br />\n但有一小撮人知法犯法，<br />\n進入商場後行使用暴力、武器，<br />\n破壞社會安寧。<br />\n<br />\n巿民眼見人多擠迫，秩序混亂，<br />\n於危急關頭，見義勇為，<br />\n以最克制武力制止騷動，<br />\n避免發生人踩人慘劇，<br />\n令商場回復平靜安全。<br />\n<br />\n各位無名義仕，<br />\n果斷勇敢保護無數平民，<br />\n好人一生平安！！！"},{"pid":"3c252e9ea65ba8f1aaac9d12e217f6609ea2eee6","tid":1319441,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T08:58:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a40762e672bdfcdffb86514d999d0bc29bcf93f6","tid":1319441,"uid":261166,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:07:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/27743445015/posts/10157742162985016?s=627332329&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F27743445015%2Fposts%2F10157742162985016%3Fs%3D627332329%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=Nl%2Bce6%2FxXxAB2W4e8qnvdodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=b539a3b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/27743445015/posts/10157742162985016?s=627332329&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你係現場，你諗番成件事你就知道其實佢地由一開始就無諗過比你走，佢由包抄果一下已經有組織咁趕你去沙田市中心然後困住你。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大家睇下個部署，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">封路，圍堵，停火車，落閘，放狗</span></span>！<br />\n只差一點，就開始了<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屠殺</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n散仔盲目執行屠城任務而不自知，<br />\n同六四入天安門新兵無分別！"},{"pid":"2f54a441cd701f65b1925ca2a5dbd76520710900","tid":1319441,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:12:46.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b26fc9e6f9f0f23221e82189bbd4fca54a81571e","tid":1319441,"uid":157516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:14:56.000Z","msg":"戰術問題，群眾都可以反包抄佢，路都係個幾條"},{"pid":"5ade59500172cc8ec9b157a8ccca3c46459913f6","tid":1319441,"uid":194403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:17:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ab21ff9594edb7020cb24446ef47d6f426b0ee2","tid":1319441,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:18:34.000Z","msg":"根本就係屠殺"},{"pid":"e2ef008ba3338bfadab133d764d5144797169df2","tid":1319441,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b26fc9e6f9f0f23221e82189bbd4fca54a81571e","tid":1319441,"uid":157516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:14:56.000Z","msg":"戰術問題，群眾都可以反包抄佢，路都係個幾條"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T01:36:29.000Z","msg":"天佑我城，港共兩次屠殺行動失敗！<br />\n儈子手政權仲可以橫行無忌，天怒人怨也！"},{"pid":"a84b86905485040ecd5aded427e42d04c8e4035d","tid":1319441,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:46:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190716/20730456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190716%2F20730456&d=Nl%2Bce6%2FxXxAB2W4e8qnvdodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=07112874\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190716%2F20730456&h=efa1ec1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190716/20730456</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好學術化乜「沸水戰術」！<br />\n實際上係會有引致人踩人慘劇的危險！"},{"pid":"df3224cd5aa2cda281e558a4a886e84287eb2411","tid":1319441,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:46:59.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"fc1efbb3e3ee345f1d8f0ccee9b4f3cee06f34ff","tid":1319441,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:48:22.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"b317603ad4e20084646369bebb970ffd4b04aa14","tid":1319441,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:15:44.000Z","msg":"一定要時刻警惕！<br />\n點樣可以杜絕慘劇發生的可能性？"},{"pid":"999c91c4b28df5e19242b107079e9aa5a403ec82","tid":1319441,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b317603ad4e20084646369bebb970ffd4b04aa14","tid":1319441,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:15:44.000Z","msg":"一定要時刻警惕！<br />\n點樣可以杜絕慘劇發生的可能性？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:12:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469061-20190718.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469061-20190718.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Nl%2Bce6%2FxXxAB2W4e8qnvdodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=c51c231a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469061-20190718.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fe4949d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469061-20190718.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員涂謹申去信特首林鄭月娥，建議對方考慮根據《警隊條例》第4條給予警務處處長指示，為往後處理示威執行警務行動時，定下政治底線，<span style=\"color: red;\">例如在整體大致和平的群眾集結中，</span>即使技術上有堵路，<span style=\"color: red;\">都不容許出現死亡或嚴重受傷的情況</span>，令警方部署時作適切考慮，只驅散不圍捕，或者讓示威者延長集會遊行。<br />\n<br />\n涂謹申說，九龍及沙田兩次遊行後出現嚴重警民衝突，都是在示威者撤退之際，警方以圍堵方式清場造成。他說，警務行動由處長級人員和現場指揮官負責，但林鄭月娥作為特首及最高政治領袖，應知道政治問題必須政治解決，她解決不到政治問題，將警隊成為政治磨心，特首不能再迴避責任。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港人最終會勝利，警察唔好站錯邊。<br />\n如果幫暴政做屠夫，終歸要落地獄！"},{"pid":"1ef05a00be2e7beb11c8bb2a71e891b5a115e2ed","tid":1319441,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:12:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">721見呀！！！！ 起碼俾返100萬人我呀！！！！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n突發！！！！ ]  荷蘭首都大學、意大利米蘭街頭 分別驚見 林鄭壽終正寢 街招！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1329216\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1329216</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">荷蘭</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/1080/https://na.cx/i/nNQk9Fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F1080%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnNQk9Fe.jpg&h=5971b37f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">意大利</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg8-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/67260952_2334870509933092_2471868942885322752_n.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQkOaykJcWH9Wa5gUItjj08X6dcp8r3HK5_qNCEeSXnxjg_dHKav3hwm2FiACInNlK8&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg8-1.fna&amp;oh=a1c45d97e8e22774df7d25b943c4a7dc&amp;oe=5DECEFD7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg8-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F67260952_2334870509933092_2471868942885322752_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQkOaykJcWH9Wa5gUItjj08X6dcp8r3HK5_qNCEeSXnxjg_dHKav3hwm2FiACInNlK8%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg8-1.fna%26oh%3Da1c45d97e8e22774df7d25b943c4a7dc%26oe%3D5DECEFD7&h=56d1a4a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/1080/https://serving.photos.photobox.com/928067831b471809fec84560cf12f81a4d43a939e63327e60d44b8c434697b1bd6e14a35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F1080%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fserving.photos.photobox.com%2F928067831b471809fec84560cf12f81a4d43a939e63327e60d44b8c434697b1bd6e14a35.jpg&h=23c7c688&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">個QR code會link去下面條片</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6_RdnVtfZPY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6_RdnVtfZPY&d=Nl%2Bce6%2FxXxAB2W4e8qnvdodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=5d2b69d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6_RdnVtfZPY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">海外手足 / 準備去旅行 /或者香港本地既 print定幫手貼</span></span><