，當然要提醒/警告警方有法律同道德責任用最低武力, 最小傷害!<br />\n<br />\n事發事，巴絲自衞自救係必須。"},{"pid":"6d98a676027a385cc673d5a6714bae8917beb684","tid":1319441,"uid":280518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T10:22:01.000Z","msg":"屌 cls"},{"pid":"56aa9f90d0ec169bc39632b75e250263e88707bc","tid":1319441,"uid":218211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:20:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33f8fe68ca7443e1313fbe2ade589c94b81cf6c9","tid":1319441,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:39:26.000Z","msg":"獨立調查委員會"}]}